ZH: 追求幸福是每个人的权利。
EN: The pursuit of happiness is everyone's right.

ZH: 我们应该追求自己的梦想。
EN: We should chase after our dreams.

ZH: 这个团队一直在追求卓越。
EN: This team has been pursuing excellence.

ZH: 她追求着内心的平静和宁静。
EN: She pursues inner peace and tranquility.

ZH: 他追求学术成就，努力进修。
EN: He pursues academic achievements and strives for further education.

ZH: 这个公司追求创新，不断推出新产品。
EN: This company pursues innovation and constantly launches new products.

ZH: 他追求财富，努力工作、投资。
EN: He pursues wealth by working hard and investing.

ZH: 这座城市追求环境友好型发展。
EN: This city pursues environmentally friendly development.

ZH: 她追求浪漫的爱情故事。
EN: She pursues romantic love stories.

ZH: 这个孩子追求知识，喜欢阅读各种书籍。
EN: This child pursues knowledge and enjoys reading various books.

ZH: 这个俱乐部追求全球化，招募了许多外国球员。
EN: This club pursues globalization and has recruited many foreign players.

ZH: 他追求名利，令人有些担忧。
EN: He pursues fame and fortune, which is somewhat worrisome.

ZH: 这个家庭追求简约生活，拒绝过度消费。
EN: This family pursues a minimalist lifestyle and rejects excessive consumption.

ZH: 她追求体验不同文化，去过多个国家旅行。
EN: She pursues the experience of different cultures and has traveled to many countries.

ZH: 这个学校注重学生追求自由思考的能力。
EN: This school emphasizes students' pursuit of the ability to think freely.

ZH: 这个社会追求平等和公正。
EN: This society pursues equality and justice.

ZH: 他追求个人成就，从不满足于现状。
EN: He pursues personal achievements and is never satisfied with the status quo.

ZH: 她追求艺术创作，每天都在画画。
EN: She pursues artistic creation and paints every day.

ZH: 这个组织追求协作与团队精神。
EN: This organization pursues collaboration and team spirit.

ZH: 我们追求的是真爱和幸福。
EN: What we pursue is true love and happiness.
